                        <interp inst="t18640711-698-verdict-1" type="verdictSubcategory" value="no_subcategory"></interp>GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.—<hi rend="italic">He was further charged with having been before convicted, at Liverpool, in March,</hi> 1857, <hi rend="italic">
when he was sentenced to Six Years' Penal Servitude; to which he</hi>
               </p>
